Package NLP.DomainOperationsFinders

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DomainOperationFinder
    Interface for Classes able to determine if a domain and his operation are involved in a sentence.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Word2vecDOFinder
    DomainFinder that uses word2vec + WordNet to determine similarities between the sentence and Domain,Operation Sentence word order is not taken into account, the method is based on multiple word similarities
    Word2vecDOFinderTest
